Fleeing the desertificiation of the world, explorers launched themselves into the void

Civilization on Earth ended, and our story began

Rescued by a mysterious alien race, humans colonized the galaxy

But they had other plans for us, and a great war protected our children but left the sectors in darkness, our planets alone and isolated

Three great civilizations rose from the ashes, each claiming to be the heritors of Earth

When once a guiding spirit made them stand together, now it makes them fall apart

Can a freighter captain heal the rifts that have formed, or will that pebble cause their annihilation?
